&lt;li&gt;Partner with marketing to define and build product capabilities that support demand generation and measurable business growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with customer success teams to identify friction, unlock growth opportunities, and drive adoption, engagement, and retention&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shape and influence the broader platform roadmap, raising the bar on quality, scalability, and capability across the business&lt;/li&gt;
